  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The claim is made today that the\nlocal liquor dealers association is\nto meet in the near future for the\npurpose of discussing the better\nment of the business and how best\nto put it upon higher plane. This\nis to be done in hope of in a meas\nure checking the prohibition move\nment to some extent. The SpO-\nkane liquor men are to work in\nconcert with those of other cities,\nall having in mind the same end\nthat of opposing the prohibitionists\nby \"elevatins\" the saloon business."
    }
